{"tid":1363493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲猶豫緊出席726機場集會既同我入黎","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T03:24:05.000Z","uid":118850,"like":187,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a56a395277c9345c24fae57bf7334b81559a18","tid":1363493,"uid":118850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"我係一個前線空管主任<br />\n今次成個香港抗爭行動無大臺<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n所以我想講<br />\n每一個同事行出黎，出席機場集會真係好重要<br />\n宜家唔係叫你罷工<br />\n正係叫你過黎機場坐下，咁都驚？<br />\n如果聽日要番工既咪早少少番工<br />\n或者收工後兜一轉機場<br />\nDayoff 既過黎搵同事食飯又得<br />\n<br />\n呢個六月同七月<br />\n香港人已經為呢個城市做左好多野，流過好多血<br />\n到早幾日，終於見到有自己部門既同事出左聲明<br />\n我感動到喊<br />\n估唔到身邊同事<br />\n作為公務員，甚至係相對上年紀大既公務員<br />\n都勇於出聲<br />\n聽日，再有一個平台俾大家明示自己既立場<br />\n俾大家影響身邊既同事，影響身邊既人<br />\n你肯出黎，可能最後令到身邊十個政治冷感，活係自己安舒區既同事反省。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再冷漠<br />\n唔好再話驚影響自己既專業形象<br />\n我想講<br />\n你先係香港人<br />\n然後先再係 ATCO，pilot，crew，operations officer。。。。<br />\n可能你無仔女係和平集會時俾警察打過<br />\n可能你唔係住元朗<br />\n可能你覺得自己揸住個牌，有咩事咪走去外國做<br />\n可能你覺得番工時 touch wood 出事會俾人送番大陸調查係無限上綱<br />\n可能講到尾 you don&rsquo;t fucking care<br />\n但如果調番轉<br />\n上面講既野真係發生係你身上<br />\n你想唔想有身邊既同事，有香港人支持你？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係政務官，支筆唔勁<br />\n但以上所講既全部都出自真心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日，約定你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Empy2Eo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmpy2Eo.png&h=f40bd4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crGQ4SK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrGQ4SK.png&h=a1cc022a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6h21r55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6h21r55.png&h=65060b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ih9ORxM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fih9ORxM.png&h=d66ac4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後，呢個係俾果d好堅持要證明我自己係唔係空管主任既人參考</span>"},{"pid":"272bba448463e0334a6200a5ac246f61dff4ca89","tid":1363493,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:57:29.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《生於亂世，有種責任》</span></span><br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f545a2410f409604dea3bb4ce6a709077e257eb2","tid":1363493,"uid":62011,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"既然機場集會係和平集會，但唔代表我地一班人坐係到鳩叫口號就算。 我地有好多有創意既宣傳手法，其中可以參考：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/faVeNam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfaVeNam.jpg&h=8084a194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n<br />\n5-8個人圍成一圈，手上可以揸IPAD/NOTEBOOK/紙標語/傳單。<br />\n<br />\n對外原地站立，輪班制，企得耐就換人，休息。<br />\n<br />\n分散係機場唔同位置，唔好分散太遠，免得有事難支援。有事發生既話隨時流動，唔好死守一地方，散完再聚。<br />\n<br />\n一組最好有一兩個英文/外語好既人，方便同旅客解釋發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳品可以放係附近，方便派發。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳內容：<br />\n可以有反修例<br />\n黑警暴力<br />\n元朗恐襲<br />\n6-7月發生既事<br />\n<br />\n語言：英文為主。<br />\n呢個方法夠曬和平，機場特警都吹你唔漲。"},{"pid":"588a239fd946ee93e030dd11c71be4cd90a3a116","tid":1363493,"uid":265877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"432e5877ca89b8efabe2aa0bae0c15ef110847d3","tid":1363493,"uid":265877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ecf3bb99d3cc4378eff32dcbacf03a56affbd30","tid":1363493,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"和你飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b3a9924eff2416a54c63c747eeba36241c09d8","tid":1363493,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:07:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">實會黎<br />\n全力支援</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a17a3918b7d964af622bab81b208a74e0963fe7c","tid":1363493,"uid":287844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\nLa La La La La La La La<br />\n鼓起這勇氣 跨出這距離<br />\n差一點我們也會飛</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0a70f9e74a2d7964632c5ba595c6531b795086f3","tid":1363493,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f4e747ae8329ba5fa669375e725642bfb997b0","tid":1363493,"uid":34924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ed6466f653e5211de1f953664416ff98d79c3e","tid":1363493,"uid":263117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"[更正] 7月26 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請大家支持！！！"},{"pid":"141dd9adc88b0500abbbf076123f1cad9bdd3eaa","tid":1363493,"uid":227748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"ATC真係香港良心！"},{"pid":"84c8005e8a1e991403d41a16f720fbfdb3d88821","tid":1363493,"uid":272458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"撐你"},{"pid":"b792440a7696b85d7a747697f7250530f1ca35da","tid":1363493,"uid":39717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"聽日見！"},{"pid":"bf90aec441eb7edf7d0d48f31de89508e4f9cd7c","tid":1363493,"uid":16689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201